law.text:
As used in this chapter, unless the context clearly requires otherwise:
"Cabinet" means the Education and Workforce Development Cabinet;
"Secretary" means the secretary of the Education and Workforce Development Cabinet or his or her duly authorized representative; and
"Commission" means the unemployment insurance commission.
law.history: Amended 2009 Ky. Acts ch. 11, sec. 69, effective June 25, 2009. -- Amended 2006 Ky. Acts ch. 211, sec. 132, effective July 12, 2006. -- Amended 1996 Ky. Acts ch. 271, sec. 13, effective July 15, 1996. -- Amended 1974 Ky. Acts ch. 74, Art. VI, sec. 95. -- Created 1950 Ky. Acts ch. 206, sec. 1.
